{"tid":1061031,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"奇景！美斯拿滿分C.朗拿度評分卻變了 這麼改有理嗎？","createTime":"2019-03-14T06:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T07:22:01.000Z","uid":173952,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fdd0480e256fd92e2bc6926bea6ac057df9017ef","tid":1061031,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:28:52.000Z","msg":"C.朗拿度和美斯在評分上一較高下<br />\n<br />\n  在這個歐冠盃比賽周中，C.朗拿度和美斯無疑是最耀眼的兩位巨星。C.朗拿度史詩般攻入3球帶領祖記逆轉馬體會，成為英雄；美斯2球2助攻統治比賽率巴塞晉級，兩人的表現都出色到了極致，也讓關羽「C.朗拿度和美斯這次誰更牛」的討論更加激烈。有趣的是，這一次連專業的評分機構也通過「騷操作」參與了進來。<br />\n<br />\nC.朗拿度昨天還是9.8分<br />\n<br />\n今天就變10分了<br />\n<br />\n  在C.朗拿度率祖記逆轉馬體會的比賽後，專業足球數據網站《<a href=\"http://Whoscored.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FWhoscored.com&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=99f9e22c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Whoscored.com</a>》給攻入全部3粒入球的C.朗拿度打出9.8分的超級高分。但在今天淩晨，晚一天比賽的美斯送出2球2助攻的表現，《<a href=\"http://Whoscored.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FWhoscored.com&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=99f9e22c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Whoscored.com</a>》直接給阿根廷人打出了10分的滿分。<br />\n<br />\n  看到這裡，你以為《<a href=\"http://Whoscored.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FWhoscored.com&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=99f9e22c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Whoscored.com</a>》認定美斯的表現強於C.朗拿度了嗎？不不不。在美斯獲得10分的滿分後，<span style=\"color: red;\">《<a href=\"http://Whoscored.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FWhoscored.com&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=99f9e22c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Whoscored.com</a>》竟然回過頭去將昨天比賽的C.朗拿度評分提高了0.2分，也湊成了10分</span>，同美斯並駕齊驅。"},{"pid":"4c2b13d3db99b57d74e75506740fe60892aaa853","tid":1061031,"uid":173952,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:29:26.000Z","msg":"其實佢出9.8時我都諗果0.2去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21ef8bceb799d2d3128023870073dbe9118d76d","tid":1061031,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:30:10.000Z","msg":"其實美斯都9.8咪無咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb22f9edb2c7508c26e21730b9403fa7aea2cc2","tid":1061031,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />專業改分員?"},{"pid":"8fe2244b0b2c8965053a71336f9feeaf0c9cfdc4","tid":1061031,"uid":10757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"怕撚左班球迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e325e6a5fb73a1675e5490b3fab6da77c32a494","tid":1061031,"uid":166126,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:43:09.000Z","msg":"不不不(nonono)"},{"pid":"a2fe42aee6ae1ab876954e6176a564453625bfd3","tid":1061031,"uid":17057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fe2244b0b2c8965053a71336f9feeaf0c9cfdc4","tid":1061031,"uid":10757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"怕撚左班球迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:46:10.000Z","msg":"可能畀分嗰位嘅同事就係牙朗同花迷，得失同事會出事架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67655d97c2c188da2abdd9eb87991447d4d76ba","tid":1061031,"uid":36724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2fe42aee6ae1ab876954e6176a564453625bfd3","tid":1061031,"uid":17057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fe2244b0b2c8965053a71336f9feeaf0c9cfdc4","tid":1061031,"uid":10757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"怕撚左班球迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"rep